This is the entropia "adventure". It show the usage of adventure QR
codes.  They are created for an adventure and are meant to be placed
in the physical world. You can create them by clicking on the
"Adventure QR codes" tab on the adventure edit screen.

This adventure consist of 4 QR codes hidden in a local hackerspace
(entropia.de).  Players try to find all 4 QR codes using the hints
provided. Once a player has scanned all of them, a victory message
is displayed.
